@startuml
title Diagrama de Sequencia - Agendamento de Servico

actor Cliente
boundary "View Thymeleaf" as View
control "AgendamentoController" as Controller
control "AgendamentoService" as Service
control "TipoServicoService" as TipoService
database "MongoDB Atlas" as Mongo

Cliente -> View: Seleciona servico, placa, data e hora
View -> Controller: POST /agendamentos
Controller -> Mongo: Busca cliente pelo e-mail autenticado
Mongo --> Controller: Cliente
Controller -> Service: agendar(cliente, tipoServicoId, placa, inicio)
Service -> TipoService: buscar(tipoServicoId)
TipoService -> Mongo: Consulta tipo de servico
Mongo --> TipoService: TipoServico
TipoService --> Service: TipoServico
Service -> Service: Calcula fim = inicio + duracao
Service -> Mongo: Procura agendamentos sobrepostos
Mongo --> Service: Lista de conflitos
alt Sem conflito
  Service -> Mongo: Salva agendamento
  Mongo --> Service: Agendamento salvo
  Service --> Controller: Sucesso
  Controller --> View: Redirect /agendamentos
else Com conflito
  Service --> Controller: Erro de horario indisponivel
  Controller --> View: Mostra mensagem de erro
end
@enduml
